  "commitMessage": "Anchor clamped windows to the snap edge instead of leaving a gap (#1778)\n\n* Add ClampedWindowAligner pure placement helper with tests\n\n* Route FixedSizeWindowMover through ClampedWindowAligner (fix half-snap edge anchoring)\n\n* Add EdgeAlignmentWindowMover to standard chain (fix FaceTime gap on half snaps)\n\n* Document moveFixedSizeToEdge flag",
